<paragraph base="F7282969" principles="no" id="IFRS01_D5"><paranum>D5</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 1"/><data name="paranum" value="D5"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS01_P0521">An entity may elect to measure an item of property, plant and equipment at the <xref base="F7282728" href="IFRS01_APPA.dita#IFRS01_APPA/IFRS01_P0223">date of transition to IFRSs<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0071"/></ph></xref> at its <xref base="F7282730" href="IFRS01_APPA.dita#IFRS01_APPA/IFRS01_DI0003" scope="local">fair value<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0118"/></ph></xref> and use that fair value as its <xref base="F7282729" href="IFRS01_APPA.dita#IFRS01_APPA/IFRS01_P0224">deemed cost<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0074"/></ph></xref> at that date.</p></body></paragraph>